Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: test-tools
Version: 0.0.3
Summary: Tools for unit testing: data_provider and FixtureManager
Home-page: https://github.com/ygavenchuk/test-tools
Author: y.gavenchuk aka murminathor
Author-email: murminathor@gmail.com
License: Apache2
Description: # Test-tools
        
        
        ## Usage
        
        Test files in project
        
            /tests
                __init__.py
                /pkg1
                    /fixtures
                        foo1.json
                        foo2.json
                    __init__.py
                    test1.py
                /pkg2
                    /fixtures
                        bar1.json
                        bar2.json
                    __init__.py
                    test2.py
        
        
        Content of "**tests/pkg1/fixtures/foo1.json**":
        
        ```javascript
        
            {
                "blah1": [
                    ["foo"],
                    ["bar"],
                    [1],
                    [2],
                    [true],
                    [null]
                ],
                "blah2": [
                    [-1234, 0],
                    [3456, -2.345],
                    [1, 1],
                    [99999, false],
                    [11, 789],
                    [null, null]
                ]
            }
        ```
        
        Content of "**tests/pkg1/test1**":
        
        ```python 
        
            from unittest import TestCase
            
            from test_tools import data_provider, FixtureManager
            
            fx_man1 = FixtureManager()
            fx_man1.load(fixture_file='foo1')
            
            fx_man2 = FixtureManager()
            fx_man2.load(fixture_file='foo2')
            
            
            class MyTestCase(TestCase):
                @data_provider(fx_man1['blah1'])
                def test_my_cool_feature(self, param1):
                    # some code
                    pass
                    
                @data_provider(fx_man1['blah2'])
                def test_my_cool_feature(self, param1, param2):
                    # some code
                    pass
                    
                @data_provider(fx_man2['blah3'])
                def test_my_cool_feature(self, param):
                    # some code
                    pass
        ```     
        
